name: gmpx-js-sample-app

scripts.start: cd src; sed -i 's/'YOUR_API_KEY'/'$MAPS_API_KEY'/g' index.html; cd ..; wds --node-resolve --open --watch

description: This directory contains a simple JS app that helps users locate a college in the US or Canada on a map, with place info such as ratings, photos, and reviews displayed on the side.
